---
slug: "fleet"
permalink: "/es/fleet/index.html"
title: "Flota | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Clases de vehículos de Morrison Premium Transfer: sedan ejecutivo, SUV premium, minivan, vans — para formatos de viaje específicos."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Flota", path: "/es/fleet/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker">{{ t.fleetPage.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1>{{ t.fleetPage.title }}</h1>
    <p class="lead">{{ t.fleetPage.lead }}</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/es/contact/">{{ t.fleetPage.bookCta }}</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fleet-grid">
      {%- for veh in fleet.classes %}
      <a class="fleet-card" href="/es/fleet/{{ veh.id }}/">
        <div class="fleet-card-head">
          <h3>{{ veh.nameEs }}</h3>
          <div class="fleet-stats">
            <span><strong>{{ veh.pax }}</strong> plazas</span>
            <span><strong>{{ veh.bags }}</strong> maletas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="fleet-examples">{{ veh.examplesEs }}</p>
        <p class="fleet-for"><strong>Para:</strong> {{ veh.forEs }}</p>
        <p class="fleet-features"><strong>Incluido:</strong> {{ veh.featuresEs }}</p>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="muted" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">{{ t.fleetPage.note }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>¿Elegir vehículo para la ruta?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/es/contact/">Abrir la solicitud</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
